{
  "id": "67062fa3b43d3d001cbb8f46",
  "title": "頭悪そうな文体",
  "created": 1728458662,
  "updated": 1730846558,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "67062fa3b43d3d001cbb8f46",
      "text": "頭悪そうな文体",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728458662,
      "updated": 1728458662
    },
    {
      "id": "6706311d71b3c20000e33c64",
      "text": "[文体]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728459036,
      "updated": 1728459038
    },
    {
      "id": "6706460571b3c20000d8fd2a",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]さんによる定義",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464387,
      "updated": 1728464532
    },
    {
      "id": "670639565b98c20000d8b3a8",
      "text": " 一人称が変 （例：ワイ）",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728461143,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "670664c979d3a90000090b00",
      "text": " \t[猛虎弁]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1728472266,
      "updated": 1728472266
    },
    {
      "id": "67062fd171b3c20000e33c5e",
      "text": " 語尾に変な文字列を付け加える（例：ンゴ）",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728458704,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "670639845b98c20000d8b3a9",
      "text": " 文語ではなく口語を使う",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728461189,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "670639d45b98c20000d8b3aa",
      "text": " 敬語を使わない、または意図的に間違った使い方をする",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728461269,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "670639f35b98c20000d8b3ab",
      "text": " スラングを多用する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728461300,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "67063a8a5b98c20000d8b3ad",
      "text": " 絵文字を多用する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728461451,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "67064f0e5b98c200007f5b06",
      "text": "['_ ここから下は[suto3.icon]が書いたものではありません]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1728466702,
      "updated": 1728466893
    },
    {
      "id": "6706450971b3c20000d8fd1f",
      "text": " \t[おじさん構文]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464136,
      "updated": 1728464409
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd2b",
      "text": " Example by AI",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464405
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd2c",
      "text": "  >ワイ、マジで今日バイト行きたくないンゴ😫",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464411
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd2d",
      "text": "  > めっちゃ疲れてるし、上司もウザいし最悪やわ🙄",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464411
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd2e",
      "text": "  > でもさ、金欲しいから仕方ないよね〜💸",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464411
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd2f",
      "text": "  > バイト終わったらマック行って爆食いしようかな🍔🍟",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464411
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd30",
      "text": "  > ヤバいって、もう時間じゃん！遅刻したらヤバイから走るわ🏃‍♂️💨",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464411
    },
    {
      "id": "6706461571b3c20000d8fd31",
      "text": "  > あーあ、人生つらたんだわ〜😭",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464404,
      "updated": 1728464411
    },
    {
      "id": "67063a395b98c20000d8b3ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1728461370,
      "updated": 1728461370
    },
    {
      "id": "6706463871b3c20000d8fd32",
      "text": "[Perplexity.icon]による定義",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464438,
      "updated": 1728464447
    },
    {
      "id": "6706464071b3c20000d8fd33",
      "text": " [長い文章]: 一文がだらだらと続く。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464447,
      "updated": 1728464495
    },
    {
      "id": "6706466571b3c20000d8fd4c",
      "text": " 論理の飛躍: 文同士のつながりが不明確。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464483,
      "updated": 1728464484
    },
    {
      "id": "6706466571b3c20000d8fd4d",
      "text": " 同じ言葉の繰り返し: 簡単な言葉ばかり使う。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464483,
      "updated": 1728464484
    },
    {
      "id": "6706466571b3c20000d8fd4e",
      "text": " 的外れな比喩: わかりにくい例えを使う。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464483,
      "updated": 1728464484
    },
    {
      "id": "6706466571b3c20000d8fd4f",
      "text": " 接続詞の不足: 文の流れが悪い。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464483,
      "updated": 1728464484
    },
    {
      "id": "6706466571b3c20000d8fd50",
      "text": " 誤字脱字が多い: 読みにくい文章。",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464483,
      "updated": 1728464484
    },
    {
      "id": "6706470971b3c20000d8fd54",
      "text": " example by ai",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464648,
      "updated": 1728464651
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474071b3c20000d8fd5f",
      "text": " \t>今日はさ、なんか天気がめっちゃいいから、外に遊びに行きたい気分なんよね☀️  ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464702,
      "updated": 1728464723
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474071b3c20000d8fd60",
      "text": "  > でも、家でゴロゴロするのも最高だし、どっちにしようかな〜って迷ってるわ🤔  ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464703,
      "updated": 1728464723
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474071b3c20000d8fd61",
      "text": "  > 友達に連絡してみたけど、みんな忙しいって言ってるし、ちょっとさみしいわ😢  ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464703,
      "updated": 1728464723
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474071b3c20000d8fd62",
      "text": "  > まあ、結局はお菓子食べながらYouTube見るのが一番楽しいかも🍿📺  ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464703,
      "updated": 1728464723
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474071b3c20000d8fd63",
      "text": "  > あー、でも外に出たら美味しいアイス食べられるし、悩むな〜🍦  ",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464703,
      "updated": 1728464723
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474071b3c20000d8fd64",
      "text": "  > 人生ってほんと選択肢多すぎて困るわ〜😂",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464703,
      "updated": 1728464723
    },
    {
      "id": "6706474871b3c20000d8fd65",
      "text": "   いい感じ[bsahd.icon][rtree.icon]",
      "userId": "66ec10e5f6246b001c4e93b1",
      "created": 1728464710,
      "updated": 1728472349
    },
    {
      "id": "6706467771b3c20000d8fd52",
      "text": " [bsahd.icon]的にはこっちの定義のほうが[Scrapbox、体裁という行為が一切ないのが良い]にあっている気がする",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464501,
      "updated": 1728464517
    },
    {
      "id": "6706518a71b3c20000d8fd70",
      "text": " [https://honyoko.blogspot.com/2017/08/20170827.html 頭の悪そうな文章の書き方口座]参考になる[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467336,
      "updated": 1728467341
    },
    {
      "id": "6706532271b3c20000d8fd81",
      "text": "  [ai.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467744,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd72",
      "text": "   > 誤変換を利用する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd73",
      "text": "   > 慣用表現を間違える",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd74",
      "text": "   > 無駄な表現を使う",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd75",
      "text": "   > 敬語を誤用する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd76",
      "text": "   > 接続詞を不適切に使う",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd77",
      "text": "   > あいまいな表現を多用する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd78",
      "text": "   > 文章の意味を曖昧にする",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd79",
      "text": "   > 不適切な例え話を使う",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd7a",
      "text": "   > リズムを崩す",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd7b",
      "text": "   > 全体の構成を乱す",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd7d",
      "text": "   > 「ので」や「が」を複数回使う",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd7e",
      "text": "   > 「なぜなら」の使い方を工夫する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706531f71b3c20000d8fd7f",
      "text": "   > 「要するに」の後に長々と説明する",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728467741,
      "updated": 1728467750
    },
    {
      "id": "6706464671b3c20000d8fd47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728464452,
      "updated": 1728464452
    },
    {
      "id": "67065a9cc84971000032833b",
      "text": "「頭が悪そう」とは誰も思わないだろうけど、[頭悪そうな文体#6706532271b3c20000d8fd81]の特徴と一致するもの",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469661,
      "updated": 1728469724
    },
    {
      "id": "6706596bc849710000328338",
      "text": "\t\t[万葉仮名][kbyshwtn.icon]",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469355,
      "updated": 1728470218
    },
    {
      "id": "67065ae1c84971000032833c",
      "text": "\t\t\t「誤変換」や「無駄な表現」、「リズムを崩す」に近いところがある",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469729,
      "updated": 1728469733
    },
    {
      "id": "67065ae5c84971000032833d",
      "text": "\t\t\t当時の人の目に「頭が悪そうな言葉遣い」に映った可能性は否めない",
      "userId": "61e1959b21ba53001f538895",
      "created": 1728469733,
      "updated": 1730846558
    },
    {
      "id": "67065af0c84971000032833e",
      "text": "\t\t\t最古の和歌がそれで書かれているので読み解かないわけにはいかなかった、という歴史は考慮する必要がある",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469745,
      "updated": 1728470298
    },
    {
      "id": "67065b0dc849710000328340",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469773,
      "updated": 1728469794
    },
    {
      "id": "67065a96c84971000032833a",
      "text": "これ（[頭悪そうな文体#6706460571b3c20000d8fd2a]）はその人の属するクラスタ（社会集団、階級など）に独特な習慣としての文体であって、それを「頭が悪い文体」だと思ってしまうのは自分がそのクラスタなりを何らかの理由で見下しているからなのでは[kbyshwtn.icon]",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469655,
      "updated": 1728470103
    },
    {
      "id": "67065d985b98c200001e956d",
      "text": "　　見下す意図はありません。そのために「おじさん構文」やそういう表現はあえて使わないようにしています [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1728470425,
      "updated": 1728470552
    },
    {
      "id": "67065e1a5b98c200001e956e",
      "text": "　　　「頭悪そう」と「頭が悪い」は別のことだと思っています",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1728470555,
      "updated": 1728470624
    },
    {
      "id": "67066175c849710000b09b84",
      "text": "　\t　\t（把握しております[kbyshwtn.icon]、言い方が少し強かったかもしれない）",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471413,
      "updated": 1728471413
    },
    {
      "id": "67065bd0c849710000328342",
      "text": "\t自分も振る舞いで人を見下すことはあるので仕方がないことだとは思う",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469969,
      "updated": 1728470097
    },
    {
      "id": "67065c3ac849710000328343",
      "text": "\t「頭が悪い人が多いクラスタ」が存在しないとも言えないし",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728470075,
      "updated": 1728470126
    },
    {
      "id": "67065c82c849710000328344",
      "text": "\t別個の問題として、「「[身内ノリ]」的な文体をどこでも使ってしまう人」は共感力なのか想像力なのかはわからないが社会的な何かが欠如しているとは思う。",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728470146,
      "updated": 1728471002
    },
    {
      "id": "6706618fc849710000b09b91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471440,
      "updated": 1728471440
    },
    {
      "id": "67066191c849710000b09b92",
      "text": "「頭が悪そう」のニュアンス[kbyshwtn.icon]",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471441,
      "updated": 1728471463
    },
    {
      "id": "6706618ec849710000b09b8d",
      "text": "　ラフな表現としての「頭が悪そう」は侮蔑的なニュアンスが弱い",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471438,
      "updated": 1728471459
    },
    {
      "id": "6706618ec849710000b09b8e",
      "text": "　\t自嘲としてもよく使う表現ではある",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471438,
      "updated": 1728471438
    },
    {
      "id": "6706618ec849710000b09b8f",
      "text": "　\tここにニュアンス書いてあった",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471438,
      "updated": 1728471438
    },
    {
      "id": "6706618ec849710000b09b90",
      "text": "　\t\t[頭が悪い]",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728471438,
      "updated": 1728471438
    },
    {
      "id": "67065b23c849710000328341",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "657bf74fbb49870024c84971",
      "created": 1728469796,
      "updated": 1728469796
    },
    {
      "id": "670644035b98c200001e956b",
      "text": "[頭が悪いごっこ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1728463876,
      "updated": 1728463883
    },
    {
      "id": "67065bf671b3c20000d8fd8f",
      "text": "[ぷよぐやみんぐ]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728470004,
      "updated": 1728470010
    },
    {
      "id": "67065bf671b3c20000d8fd90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1728470004,
      "updated": 1728470004
    }
  ]
}